  "short_description": "LETALIS is a non-linear RPG where you train fierce warriors to fight for “Glory or Death” in coliseums ruled by Caesars. Explore mysterious lands, uncover hidden secrets and recruit over 1,000 unique Letalis. Every battle shapes your journey, every path tells a story.",
