  "detailed_description": "Meet the <strong>LETALIS</strong>, fearless warriors forged for the arena, where every battle is fought for “Glory or Death\".<br>As the Manager, you must lead your fighters to greatness and claim the title of Caesar. Travel across a vast continent and recruit powerful LETALIS to forge your legend.<br><br><strong>Forge your Own Story</strong>:<br>Embark on an epic journey across diverse lands in a non-linear adventure where the path forward is yours to choose. Battle fierce enemies, help towns in need and uncover hidden paths as you search for Coliseums where you can prove your strength.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396200/extras/12fd261540be0a540af8cab1ccc13ea4.poster.avif?t=1773968213\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396200/extras/12fd261540be0a540af8cab1ccc13ea4.webm?t=1773968213\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396200/extras/12fd261540be0a540af8cab1ccc13ea4.mp4?t=1773968213\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Prepare your Fighters</strong>:<br>Build the perfect LETALIS lineup by balancing different fighting styles and equipping the right weapons to match your strategy. Strengthen their combat skills and experiment with powerful combinations to create a playstyle that is uniquely yours.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396200/extras/53c028637c16e43b9e1148dbf48f82b8.poster.avif?t=1773968213\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396200/extras/53c028637c16e43b9e1148dbf48f82b8.webm?t=1773968213\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396200/extras/53c028637c16e43b9e1148dbf48f82b8.mp4?t=1773968213\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Prove your worth in the Arena</strong>:<br>The ultimate test of your might! Face three battles in a row where every move could be your last. Study your opponents’ patterns, exploit their lineups and claim victory against their Caesar.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396200/extras/c74910139dbc2d43a18a85e0a4eb3f8b.poster.avif?t=1773968213\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396200/extras/c74910139dbc2d43a18a85e0a4eb3f8b.webm?t=1773968213\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396200/extras/c74910139dbc2d43a18a85e0a4eb3f8b.mp4?t=1773968213\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Uncover the Realm’s Secrets</strong>:<br>Immerse yourself in the lives of its citizens to uncover hidden secrets and reveal a tangled web of political intrigue. As the truth unfolds, you’ll expose schemes of power and discover forgotten dungeons filled with ancient artifacts and untold treasures.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396200/extras/7302d8a51c7990f607b65688bcfc3811.poster.avif?t=1773968213\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396200/extras/7302d8a51c7990f607b65688bcfc3811.webm?t=1773968213\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396200/extras/7302d8a51c7990f607b65688bcfc3811.mp4?t=1773968213\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Meet the <strong>LETALIS</strong>, fearless warriors forged for the arena, where every battle is fought for “Glory or Death\".<br>As the Manager, you must lead your fighters to greatness and claim the title of Caesar. Travel across a vast continent and recruit powerful LETALIS to forge your legend.<br><br><strong>Forge your Own Story</strong>:<br>Embark on an epic journey across diverse lands in a non-linear adventure where the path forward is yours to choose. Battle fierce enemies, help towns in need and uncover hidden paths as you search for Coliseums where you can prove your strength.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396200/extras/12fd261540be0a540af8cab1ccc13ea4.poster.avif?t=1773968213\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396200/extras/12fd261540be0a540af8cab1ccc13ea4.webm?t=1773968213\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396200/extras/12fd261540be0a540af8cab1ccc13ea4.mp4?t=1773968213\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Prepare your Fighters</strong>:<br>Build the perfect LETALIS lineup by balancing different fighting styles and equipping the right weapons to match your strategy. Strengthen their combat skills and experiment with powerful combinations to create a playstyle that is uniquely yours.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396200/extras/53c028637c16e43b9e1148dbf48f82b8.poster.avif?t=1773968213\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396200/extras/53c028637c16e43b9e1148dbf48f82b8.webm?t=1773968213\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396200/extras/53c028637c16e43b9e1148dbf48f82b8.mp4?t=1773968213\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Prove your worth in the Arena</strong>:<br>The ultimate test of your might! Face three battles in a row where every move could be your last. Study your opponents’ patterns, exploit their lineups and claim victory against their Caesar.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396200/extras/c74910139dbc2d43a18a85e0a4eb3f8b.poster.avif?t=1773968213\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396200/extras/c74910139dbc2d43a18a85e0a4eb3f8b.webm?t=1773968213\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396200/extras/c74910139dbc2d43a18a85e0a4eb3f8b.mp4?t=1773968213\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Uncover the Realm’s Secrets</strong>:<br>Immerse yourself in the lives of its citizens to uncover hidden secrets and reveal a tangled web of political intrigue. As the truth unfolds, you’ll expose schemes of power and discover forgotten dungeons filled with ancient artifacts and untold treasures.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396200/extras/7302d8a51c7990f607b65688bcfc3811.poster.avif?t=1773968213\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396200/extras/7302d8a51c7990f607b65688bcfc3811.webm?t=1773968213\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396200/extras/7302d8a51c7990f607b65688bcfc3811.mp4?t=1773968213\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
